<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TOGAPhotos 审核通知</title>
</head>

<body
        style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f6f7f9; font-family: Segoe UI, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1c1c1f;">
<div style="width: 100%; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 16px 12px; box-sizing: border-box;">
    <div style="width: 100%;">

        <section
                style="padding: 20px 18px; background: #ffffff; box-shadow: none; border: 0; display: block; letter-spacing: 0.01em;">
            <div style="display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <div style="display: block;">
                    <div>
                        <img src="https://cos-125-tp-cdn.794td.cn/assets/n_logo_b.jpg" alt="TOGAPhotos" width="120"
                             style="display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;">
                    </div>
                    <div style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 8px;">
                        审核结果提醒</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="height: 1px; width: 100%; background: rgba(12, 12, 13, 0.08);">
            </div>
            <div style="color: #545454; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; margin-top: 10px;">
                {{username}},感谢您选择在TOGAPhotos上传您的作品，我们已完成对您上传作品的审核，以下是本次的审核结果：
            </div>
            <div style="display: block;">
                {{#if rejectQueue}}
                    <article
                            style="margin: 16px 0 16px 0; padding: 20px 22px; border-left: 2px solid #ff0000; background: #ffffff; color: #1c1c1f; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.05); letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: start; gap: 8px">
                        <div style="display: block;">
                            <div style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2;">强制清空上传队列</div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: block;">
                            <div style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                                说明
                            </div>
                            <div
                                    style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #1c1c1f;">
                                这是TOGAPhotos的一项惩罚措施，触发此项说明您的作品存在严重问题，请仔细阅读审核说明并避免类似问题的再次发生。
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                {{/if}}
                {{#each results}}
                    {{#if accept}}
                        <article
                                style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; padding: 20px 22px; border-left: 2px solid #2b7bff; background: #ffffff; color: #1c1c1f; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.05); letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: start;">
                            <div style="display: block;">
                                <div
                                        style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                                    图片 ID</div>
                                <div style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2;">{{id}}</div>
                            </div>
                            <div style="display: block;">
                                <div
                                        style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                                    图片信息</div>
                                <div
                                        style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #1c1c1f;">
                                    航空公司：{{airline}}</div>
                                <div
                                        style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #1c1c1f;">
                                    注册号：{{ac_reg}}</div>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                    style="display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(43, 123, 255, 0.12); color: #1a4ea2; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                                通过</div>
                        </article>
                    {{/if}}

                    {{#if reject}}
                        <article
                                style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; padding: 20px 22px; border-left: 2px solid #ffae2b; background: #ffffff; color: #1c1c1f; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.05); letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: start;">
                            <div style="display: block;">
                                <div
                                        style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                                    图片 ID</div>
                                <div style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2;">{{id}}</div>
                            </div>
                            <div style="display: block;;">
                                <div style="display: block;">
                                    <div
                                            style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                                        图片信息</div>
                                    <div
                                            style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #1c1c1f;">
                                        航空公司：{{airline}}</div>
                                    <div
                                            style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #1c1c1f;">
                                        注册号：{{ac_reg}}</div>
                                </div>
                                <div style="display: block; margin-top: 8px;">
                                    <div
                                            style="font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7a7a7a;">
                                        审核说明</div>
                                    <div
                                            style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #1c1c1f;">
                                        {{reason}}</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                    style="display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255, 170, 43, 0.14); color: #9c6100; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                                未通过</div>
                        </article>
                    {{/if}}
                {{/each}}
            </div>
            <a href="https://togaphotos.com/queue/reject"
               style="display: block; width: 80%; margin: 16px auto; padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(43, 123, 255, 0.12); color: #1a4ea2; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-decoration: none; text-align: center;">
                查看未通过审核的作品
            </a>
            <div style="color: #545454; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 12px;">
                若您的作品未通过审核，我们欢迎您在根据审核意见修改或优化后重新上传。
                <br>为保证审核流程的公平与高效，<b>TOGAPhotos不接受对审核结果的申诉</b>。
            </div>
            <div style="color: #545454; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; text-align: right;">
                <b>TOGAPhotos 内容审核团队</b>
            </div>
            <div style="height: 1px; width: 100%; background: rgba(12, 12, 13, 0.08);">
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #8a8a8a; line-height: 1.6;">
                您可以在个人设置中心关闭此通知。
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #8a8a8a; line-height: 1.6;">
                若您有疑问，请联系 support@togaphotos.com
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>